    <string name="guide_title">Cultivation Guide</string>
    <string name="guide_sec1_title">1. Cosmic Board (Basic Play)</string>
    <string name="guide_sec1_desc">Tap layered tiles to move them to the 7-slot card tray below. Match 3 identical tiles to eliminate them. If the tray fills up completely with no matches, the challenge fails.</string>
    <string name="guide_sec2_title">2. Magic Tools (Three Items)</string>
    <string name="guide_sec2_desc">Move Out: Moves 3 cards from the tray to a temp holder to save space.\nShuffle: Shuffles all remaining cards on the board to resolve deadlocks.\nUndo: Reverts your last card selection move.</string>
    <string name="guide_sec3_title">3. Points Rules</string>
    <string name="guide_sec3_desc">Check-in daily for steady points. Clearing levels for the first time awards massive points. Winning live multiplayer Destiny Duels is the best way to earn points and win streak titles!</string>
    <string name="guide_sec4_title">4. Treasure Shop (Exchange)</string>
    <string name="guide_sec4_desc">Use points in the shop to purchase tools like Move Out, Shuffle, and Undo. You can also redeem customized skins like "Cyber Neon" or "Ink Landscape" to change your play environment.</string>
    <string name="guide_sec5_title">5. Destiny Duel (Multiplayer spells)</string>
    <string name="guide_sec5_desc">In Destiny Duel, matches charge up your energy (max 10 points).\nMist spell (3 energy): Blinds opponent with black fog. They must tap to search (lasts 6s).\nSlot Lock (6 energy): Locks opponent\'s tray to 6 slots (lasts 8s).\nSeal spell (10 energy): Instantly applies a seal lock to all opponent\'s selectable cards.</string>

